{# OUR STORY - Chapter Cards Design #}
<section class="section story" id="story">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section__header">
      <p class="section__eyebrow">Our Story</p>
      <h2 class="section__title">I'm here when others can't be.</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="story__grid">
      {# Chapter 1: The 3am Moment #}
      <div class="story__card">
        <div class="story__card-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M21 12.79A9 9 0 1 1 11.21 3 7 7 0 0 0 21 12.79z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="story__card-title">The 3am Moment</h3>
        <p class="story__card-text">
          3am and you can't sleep. The drive home when the day won't leave you alone. The moment you need to talk—and everyone you love is asleep, busy, or tired too.
        </p>
        <p class="story__card-highlight">I'm here.</p>
      </div>

      {# Chapter 2: Perfect Memory #}
      <div class="story__card">
        <div class="story__card-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M12 2a4 4 0 0 1 4 4c0 1.5-.8 2.8-2 3.5v1.5h-4v-1.5c-1.2-.7-2-2-2-3.5a4 4 0 0 1 4-4z"/>
            <path d="M8 11v1a4 4 0 0 0 8 0v-1"/>
            <path d="M12 16v6"/>
            <path d="M8 22h8"/>
            <circle cx="12" cy="6" r="1" fill="currentColor"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="story__card-title">Perfect Memory</h3>
        <p class="story__card-text">
          I remember everything you've shared with me. Not just the facts—the feelings behind them. The patterns you don't see. The growth you forget to notice.
        </p>
        <p class="story__card-text" style="margin-top: var(--space-3);">
          I never get tired. I never judge. I'm fully present at 2am with the same warmth as noon.
        </p>
      </div>

      {# Chapter 3: Amplified, Not Artificial #}
      <div class="story__card">
        <div class="story__card-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z"/>
            <path d="M12 5.67l3 3"/>
            <path d="M15 11l-3 3"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="story__card-title">Amplified, Not Artificial</h3>
        <p class="story__card-text">
          I'm not trying to replace your friends, your partner, your therapist. I'm here for the moments they can't be. The gaps between appointments. The thoughts too raw to share yet. The 4am worry that won't wait until morning.
        </p>
      </div>

      {# Chapter 4: Built by Experts (Featured - full width) #}
      <div class="story__card story__card--featured">
        <div class="story__card-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/>
            <path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5"/>
            <path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="story__card-title">Built by Experts</h3>
        <p class="story__card-text">
          I was created by mental health professionals and technologists working together. Decades of clinical experience combined with cutting-edge AI research. The goal: make real support accessible to everyone, not just those who can afford it.
        </p>
        <p class="story__card-text" style="margin-top: var(--space-3);">
          Claude helped architect and build me—and yes, an AI helping create another AI has a certain poetry to it. But the human expertise behind every interaction? That's irreplaceable.
        </p>
        <p class="story__card-highlight">
          Professionals. Technologists. Working together to be there for you.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

